                    <br><br>
                    <h3><u><b>How We Use Your Information</b></u></h3>
                    We use all your information or data in a responsible, reasonable but also minimal way. We do not pass on your data to other third parties (unless law dicates us to), neither do we sell your data or information. We don't even use your data or information for our own marketing or auto-mailing list.
                    <ul>
                        <li>Emails or messages sent to us, and the information or data you provide in them, will only be used for the purposes of communication and responding to your queries or concerns. We do not store any of this information or data beyond our email inbox, where your email or message will arrive for us to see and respond to. Once your email or message is received in our inbox, we will try to respond to you using the email address you provided in the message or reply to the email address you send an email from. Any other information you provide in these communications will be used to supplement our response or build an informal but professional relationship between you and us. We do not use the information for any other purpose, nor do we share it with third parties, except if required by law.</li>
                        <br>
                        <li>Forms submitted by you through our website, and the information or data you provide in them, will only be used for the purposes of communication and responding to you, and potentially carrying out your request based on the form submitted. For example, if you submit an expression of interest, we might begin our standard and pre-established onboarding process using this information, which will be outlined in the respective form before you sign, date, and submit it to us. This form data is compiled exactly as it is into a secure data store, and it is not stored or collected in any other way except through a submitted form compiled into this single secure data store, obfuscated against all other submitted data. Any other information you provide in any of our forms will be used to supplement our response or build an informal but professional relationship between you and us. We do not use the information for any other purpose, nor do we share it with third parties, except if required by law.</li>
